race.comment: Cracking race with plenty of chances. JUST IN TIME (9) tough win first-up at Canterbury, then dug deep from the sticky draw with a courageous sixth over 1300m in the Magic Millions F&M at the Gold Coast. Kept up to the mark with a sharp 1000m trial win and can get the job done. OUI OUI OUI (2) talented mare undefeated in three runs this time in. Fitted with a searching 1207m trial win and shapes as the main danger on her home track. ROLLING MAGIC (1) tough gelding who comes out of a strong rating contest after running a respectable fourth over the mile at Randwick in BM88 grade. Undefeated at the track and will prove hard to get past. IMPOSANT (8) resumes after failing to match it in Group company early in the prep last time in. Went out a winner with a commanding victory over 1350m at Doomben last October. Given the two trials and stays in the mix.
